License:	GPL-2.0-or-later
URL:		http://xmoto.sourceforge.net/
Source0:	https://github.com/xmoto/xmoto/archive/v%{version}/%{version}.tar.gz
Source1:	xmoto.desktop
Source2:	xmoto.png
